\cf0 Overview\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa240\partightenfactor0

\f1\b0\fs24 \cf0 This project is a Movie Recommendation web app built using 
\f0\b Flask
\f1\b0 , 
\f0\b Ollama
\f1\b0 , and 
\f0\b ChromaDB
\f1\b0 . The app allows users to enter a movie-related prompt, which is processed to retrieve and explain a movie recommendation. The system uses Ollama models for natural language processing and movie-related embeddings stored in a ChromaDB collection.\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa298\partightenfactor0

\f0\b\fs36 \cf0 Prerequisites\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa240\partightenfactor0

\f1\b0\fs24 \cf0 Before running the app, ensure you have the following installed:\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\partightenfactor0
\ls1\ilvl0
\f0\b \cf0 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 Python 3.8+
\f1\b0  (Download from {\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "https://www.python.org/downloads/"}}{\fldrslt \cf3 \ul \ulc3 \strokec3 python.org}})\
\ls1\ilvl0
\f0\b \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 pip
\f1\b0  (Python package manager; should be installed with Python)\
\ls1\ilvl0
\f0\b \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 Ollama
\f1\b0  (for model access) - {\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "https://ollama.com/"}}{\fldrslt \cf3 \ul \ulc3 \strokec3 ollama.com}}\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa240\partightenfactor0
\cf0 You will also need to download the necessary models for Ollama to function correctly. This can be done through the Ollama CLI after installation.\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa298\partightenfactor0

\f0\b\fs36 \cf0 Step-by-Step Setup\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa280\partightenfactor0

\fs28 \cf0 1. Install Python\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa240\partightenfactor0

\f1\b0\fs24 \cf0 If you don't already have Python installed, download it from the official website and follow the installation instructions based on your operating system.\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa280\partightenfactor0

\f0\b\fs28 \cf0 2. Install Required Libraries\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa240\partightenfactor0

\f1\b0\fs24 \cf0 Ensure you have 
\f2\fs26 pip
\f1\fs24  installed. Open your terminal or command prompt and run the following commands to install the necessary dependencies:
\f2\fs26 \
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0
\cf0 pip install flask\
pip install chromadb\
pip install ollama\
\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa280\partightenfactor0

\f0\b\fs28 \cf0 3. Download Ollama Models\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa240\partightenfactor0

\f1\b0\fs24 \cf0 Once Ollama is installed, you need to download the models required by the app. In your terminal or command prompt, run the following commands to download the models:
\f2\fs26 \
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0
\cf0 ollama pull mistral-nemo\
ollama pull nomic-embed-text\
\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa240\partightenfactor0

\f1\fs24 \cf0 These commands pull the necessary models for generating and embedding text for movie recommendations.\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa280\partightenfactor0

\f0\b\fs28 \cf0 4. Set Up the Flask Application\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa240\partightenfactor0

\f1\b0\fs24 \cf0 Open 
\f2\fs26 movieRecommendationSystem.py
\f1\fs24  in your preferred code editor. The Flask app will be set up and ready to run. Ensure that the 
\f2\fs26 SECRET_KEY
\f1\fs24  is set to a secure value for your application\'92s session management.\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa280\partightenfactor0

\f0\b\fs28 \cf0 5. Running the Application\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa240\partightenfactor0

\f1\b0\fs24 \cf0 In your terminal, navigate to the project directory and run the following command to start the Flask server:
\f2\fs26 \
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0
\cf0 python3 movieRecommendationSystem.py\
\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa240\partightenfactor0

\f1\fs24 \cf0 This will start the Flask development server. By default, it will be accessible at 
\f2\fs26 http://127.0.0.1:5000/
\f1\fs24  in your web browser.\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa280\partightenfactor0

\f0\b\fs28 \cf0 6. Using the Application\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\partightenfactor0
\ls2\ilvl0
\f1\b0\fs24 \cf0 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 When you visit the app in your browser, you will see a prompt input field. Enter a movie-related request like \'93I want a movie with love and romance,\'94 and click the 
\f0\b Submit
\f1\b0  button.\
\ls2\ilvl0\kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 The app will process the input, query the ChromaDB, and return a movie recommendation along with an explanation.\
\ls2\ilvl0\kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
